                           <quote xml:lang="en"/> The note is possibly written in the main hand. The
                           first part is written in Amharic and contains the following genealogy:
                           ʾƎras Giyorgis, ʾƎras Zärʿat, ʿAmdom, ʾato Hagos, Gabra Masqal, blatta
                           Kasa, Bǝwaltaʾu (Gabra Mikāʾel Bǝwältaʾu is also mentioned in subscriptio
                           on <locus target="#41ra">41ra</locus>
                           <note>). The second part is written in Gǝʿǝz and states that blatta Kasa
                              donated this book to Qǝddus Qirqos ʾAd Subha. </note>
